---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Vibe Decoder - Your source for technology insights and deep dives.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] text-glow mb-4 font-mono">
        &gt; About Vibe Decoder_
      </h1>
      <div class="h-1 w-32 bg-[--color-terminal-green] mb-6"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-12">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Vibe Decoder Logo" class="h-40 w-40" />
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[--color-bg-dark-card] border border-[--color-terminal-green] p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-4 font-mono">
          :: Mission
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-light]">
          Vibe Decoder exists to empower developers to transcend syntax and focus on logic using Generative AI.
          We believe that the future of coding is not about typing characters, but about orchestrating intelligence.
          We help you master the art of "Vibe Coding"‚Äîcoding at the speed of thought.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mt-12 mb-6 font-mono">
          :: What We Cover
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-[--color-bg-dark-card] border border-[--color-terminal-green]/50 p-6 hover:border-[--color-terminal-green] transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-3 font-mono">
              ü§ñ AI Pair Programming
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-dim]">
              Mastering tools like Cursor, GitHub Copilot, and local LLMs to multiply your productivity.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[--color-bg-dark-card] border border-[--color-terminal-green]/50 p-6 hover:border-[--color-terminal-green] transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-3 font-mono">
              ‚ö° Prompt Engineering
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-dim]">
              The new syntax. Learning how to speak the language of models to get exactly what you want.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[--color-bg-dark-card] border border-[--color-terminal-green]/50 p-6 hover:border-[--color-terminal-green] transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-3 font-mono">
              ‚òÅÔ∏è Agentic Workflows
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-dim]">
              Moving beyond chat. Building autonomous agents that can plan, execute, and debug complex tasks.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[--color-bg-dark-card] border border-[--color-terminal-green]/50 p-6 hover:border-[--color-terminal-green] transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-3 font-mono">
              üîÆ LLM Internals
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-dim]">
              Understanding transformers, attention mechanisms, and context windows to be a better pilot.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[--color-bg-dark-card] border border-[--color-terminal-green] p-8 mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-4 font-mono">
          :: Why "Vibe Decoder"?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-light] mb-4">
          "Vibe Coding" is a term coined to describe the flow state achieved when you're no longer fighting the compiler, 
          but guiding an AI to build your vision. It's about the "vibe"‚Äîthe intuition, the high-level design, the soul of the software.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-light]">
          Our retro terminal aesthetic is a reminder that while the tools change, the hacker spirit remains the same. 
          We are decoding the new vibes of the AI era.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-6 font-mono">
          :: The Philosophy
        </h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-[--color-text-light]">
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="text-[--color-terminal-green] font-bold font-mono">></span>
            <span><strong class="text-[--color-terminal-green]">Logic over Syntax:</strong> Don't memorize APIs. Understand systems.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="text-[--color-terminal-green] font-bold font-mono">></span>
            <span><strong class="text-[--color-terminal-green]">Augmentation, not Replacement:</strong> AI is a bicycle for the mind. Learn to ride it.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="text-[--color-terminal-green] font-bold font-mono">></span>
            <span><strong class="text-[--color-terminal-green]">Iterate Fast:</strong> Fail faster to succeed sooner. AI allows rapid prototyping.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <span class="text-[--color-terminal-green] font-bold font-mono">></span>
            <span><strong class="text-[--color-terminal-green]">Stay Curious:</strong> The models are learning. You should be too.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-[--color-bg-dark-card] border-2 border-[--color-terminal-green] p-8 mt-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[--color-terminal-green] mb-4 font-mono">
          :: Join the Journey
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-light] mb-6">
          Technology is constantly evolving, and so are we. Check out our latest articles and join the conversation.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/blog" 
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-[--color-terminal-green] text-[--color-bg-dark] font-bold font-mono hover:bg-[--color-terminal-green-light] transition-all transform hover:scale-105"
        >
          Read Articles ‚Üí
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
